<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_35207127-2f29-4e38-9354-dbffbc0d96f4" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><sptc>E3P4</sptc><title id="_05edc296-1d18-4f2a-b692-237098c34ae9">Design, construction and installation</title><archive-num>2019: FP1.4</archive-num><subclause id="_96976a90-a410-448d-85b3-13f56471a71c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_423282ca-3f66-4273-812b-3246c97045ed">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A roof drainage system must ensure that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f2283097-260e-42e3-8fed-10c70ba8a436">stormwater is transferred to a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_668b1a4d-dd81-470c-881e-22c9d8b30ab2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator's</xref> stormwater system or an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1193_0.6.0.xml#_9d2e065b-aa41-45f9-b2f5-4628d8fa28d0" id="_63a4d231-69ac-4ee8-a64d-a4c2131e076b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">approved disposal system</xref>; and</li><li id="_2775a436-9d2b-4e4b-aac3-b877873f631e">appropriate access is provided for maintenance and clearing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_40dd63fd-2d78-43ff-9d8c-e4258952a17e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockages</xref>. </li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_feea8da3-8b1e-4733-8c29-1646688ca91d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_fbbb679f-a6b2-489a-91bc-573eb1da0634">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A roof drainage installation must avoid <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_5a34d249-2fdc-4373-8c51-498ea9959168" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockage</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1500_27.0.0.xml#_0ece1af9-d663-4f17-a7c9-bf59ebb1b1ef" id="_f068b478-9ebb-46ef-9d36-be1ee01b6ca3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">uncontrolled discharge</xref> causing—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_5bfdeea9-8ae9-46ff-9d9c-bb63efbf5c65"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_0d49a6bc-14f7-4732-beed-253cb5fce84b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_262fb65e-30f1-45e5-a81b-a270ec9bb994" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref>; and</li><li id="_7ac94884-1dce-442e-b7e7-d23df8af2975"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_87f61641-4981-490f-9390-ce2d3cd345ee" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">loss</xref> to building and property.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_939aade7-53d5-4aa1-bebd-7be91b34a295" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_82d5b2e3-d6b2-4911-98c3-89a1cc117a42">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A roof drainage installation must avoid foul air and gasses accumulating in the roof drainage system. </p></subclause></clause>